Majid Jafar, CEO of Crescent Petroleum, comments on the current situation in the Middle East region. He says stability is vital and “our region is lacking it.” 

Speaking to CNBC’s Hadley Gamble and Karen Tso from the World Economic Forum in Davos, he talks about how to tackle the climate change & discusses the U.S.-Iran conflict.

